platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Pixite 的卓越编辑工具, 可让你将逼真的 3D 物体添加到照片和视频中, 实时调节其倒影和阴影, 并通过网上社区与他人分享创意。“Matter”拥有数量繁多的华丽造型和精美背景, 还可使用立体模型的动态效果, 帮你打造与众不同的绝妙作品。

With Pixite’s incredible editor, you can add realistic 3D objects to your photos and videos, adjust everything from reflections to shadows in real time, and then share them across the internet. With a swath of impressive objects to place, a variety of sample backgrounds to test out, and the ability to animate your 3D models, Matter will make your photos and videos extraordinary.
